entries.title: Ford Follows Tesla in Cutting Electric Vehicle Prices
entries.description: The automaker reduced the price of the Mustang Mach-E by up to $5,900 after Tesla slashed prices of its cars by as much as 20 percent.

entries.title: ‘Recession Resilient’ Climate Start-Ups Shine in Tech Downturn
entries.description: Tech workers and investors are flocking to start-ups that aim to combat climate change.
